### Notification Service Smoke Tests
### Start service: PORT=8087 MONGODB_URI=mongodb://music_admin:music_pass@localhost:27017/notifications?authSource=admin RABBITMQ_URL=amqp://music_admin:music_pass@localhost:5672/music REDIS_URL=redis://:music_pass@localhost:6379 JWT_SECRET=secret pnpm nx serve @org/notification-service

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8087/api
@userId = test-user-123

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/metrics

### List notifications (no auth required via AuthGuard header)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/notifications
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### List unread only
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/notifications?unreadOnly=true
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### Get unread count
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/notifications/unread-count
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### Get preferences (creates default if not exists)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/notifications/preferences
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### Update preferences
PUT {{baseUrl}}/v1/notifications/preferences
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "emailEnabled": false,
  "newFollower": true,
  "newRelease": false
}

### Mark all as read
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/notifications/read-all
X-User-Id: {{userId}}

### Mark single notification as read (replace with real id)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/notifications/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011/read
X-User-Id: {{userId}}
